{
  "stem": "1415.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They did not look the same, like the Germans did, with the-- with the clanking of their boots.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't hardly had anything like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this-- this is my recollection of the Russian liberation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And after that, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't know how-- if it was days or nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They dressed us up in those striped uniforms, which we never had before, ever, because those were warm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they took pictures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was lucky enough-- I attached myself to one Russian soldier.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I went with them on the Jeep when they were filming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, the films that you see at the liberation of Auschwitz are unreal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And no human being can explain it, what it looked like.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'm sure you've seen the pictures.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I'm sure you saw real pictures that they show.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, this is what we were liberated with.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There were bodies everywhere that died afterwards, and those were gathered up in front of each camp and put in big piles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were lucky it was winter, so the bodies stayed intact.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were not causing any health hazards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That's what we found out later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Of course, I was a child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I didn't know all this stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "All I know is that when I went around with that Russian, and they were filming the devastation of Auschwitz with those mass graves and all these things that you only see on film, this is what we had in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And afterwards, they-- then they actually transferred us to Auschwitz, to Auschwitz, which was different.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There were not barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There were regular, like, army barracks, which were not made out of wood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were real barracks made out of something or another, but not wood.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
